The '''Spaghetti Junction''' is a step up from the [[Main/en/Cloverleaf]].  It is more complicated and expensive, but smaller and with more exits before merges.

[[File:en/Spaghetti.png|none|thumb|595px|Spaghetti junction (simple)]]

{{Template:Junction_Criteria|Expensive|3|1|0|1|1|0|1|0|0|2|0||Broken down trains only affect left hand turns in one axis.|
*Handle a large number of trains at a time.
*Functions as a U in 2 of the 4 primary directions.
*Takes up a large amount of space.
*Trains merge before they split in one axis.
*Make it so your longest train can fit completely into one of the turning tracks without blocking the main line behind it.
*Area: 16 x 16
}}

